         "id": "3ea21df7-f7c0-4341-bd2a-9ebbf8bb2228",
         "name": "Joaquina \"Cabra\"",
         "history": [
            {
               "text": "Joaquina is referred to as \"Cabra\", but this is not her surname. It was a classification used for enslaved people",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "17173373-0162-4e48-b00d-a8f7803da1ad",
                     "text": "Irffi, Ana S. R. P. C., <span class=\"htdate\"></span>, pp. 38-41"
                  },
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "21dcc2d5-af8c-4f57-96f2-16a7e8bd3493",
                     "text": "Almeida, Mayara Aparecida Ribeiro De, et al., <span class=\"htdate\"></span>"
                  }
               ],
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": "."
            }
         ],
         "people": [
            {
               "id": "3ea21df7-f7c0-4341-bd2a-9ebbf8bb2228",
               "name": "Joaquina \"Cabra\"",
               "surname": "",
               "patronymic": "",
               "fullname": "Joaquina \"Cabra\"",
               "sex": "feminine",
               "gender": "feminine",
               "is_real": true,
               "haplogroup": null,
               "history": [
                  {
                     "text": "In addition to her classification as \"Cabra\", we know she was enslaved because she is mentioned in her daughter's baptism record as: slave of Maria Úrsula (<i>\"escrava de Maria Úrsula\"</i>)",
